<p>What I have trouble understanding from the Hutton worship and Whitmore bashing, is how so many self-proclaimed pagans do not want to address the fact that that they have a long history, albeit mostly obscure.  I guess they&#8217;ve never heard the saying:  Those who don&#8217;t have a past don&#8217;t have a future.</p>
